name: You are an artist, Sun! 02
description:
►✨☀️
Round appearing,
Illuminant fire,
Built in space,
Shedding heat,
Traveling westward,
Your photosphere,
Conflicts,
With dwindling light,
Of stricken day,
At dying hour.
Emerging from,
The reek appears,
At distant edge of earth,
A straightened rainbow,
Reaching far into the sky,
You are an artist, Sun!

Raymond
